question: How do I install the "ComfyUI-Manager" extension?
answer: To install the "ComfyUI-Manager" extension, follow these steps: 1. Open the settings menu in ComfyUI. 2. Navigate to the "Extensions" section. 3. Find and select the "ComfyUI-Manager" extension. 4. Click on the "Install" button. 5. Wait for the installation to complete.
